                    <section class="l-page-block l-text-block bottom-line">
                <div class="l-content-container">
                    <h2>Health and safety</h2>
                    <div>
                        <p>At Newcastle University London, your safety is our top priority. There's a 24-hour phone number that you can call in the event of an emergency or, if you have an issue that doesn't require immediate attention, you can book an appointment with a welfare adviser.</p>
<p>We'll also make sure you know how to register with a doctor or contact the police, as part of your induction. Of course, if you have any questions or need help with anything during your time with us we're always here to help!</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        

